{
  "id": "69f3efeeda8938ab2d2b1eab",
  "title": "無理が通れば道理が引っ込むということは、道理を通せば無理が引っ込むことになる",
  "created": 1777594350,
  "updated": 1777595927,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f3efeeda8938ab2d2b1eab",
      "text": "無理が通れば道理が引っ込むということは、道理を通せば無理が引っ込むことになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777595629
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f4d900000000004bd658",
      "text": "旧タイトル：[- 無理が通れば道理が引っ込むということは、道理を通せば無理を押し込むことになる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595608,
      "updated": 1777595617
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a912c",
      "text": "from [2026/05/01]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777594350
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f54400000000004bd65a",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595715,
      "updated": 1777595716
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a912d",
      "text": " 無理が通れば道理が引っ込むということは、道理を通せば無理を押し込むことになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777594350
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a912e",
      "text": " [ロジハラ]というやつに当たりそうにみえて[ヒヤヒヤ.icon]してます[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777595720
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a912f",
      "text": " 無理を通す時にロジックで押し通そうとするのが[ロジハラ]じゃないかな[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777595720
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a9130",
      "text": " もう少し広そうだと思ってます。[ロジハラ]ページを作った[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777595720
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a9131",
      "text": " \t[り.icon][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777595720
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a9132",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777594350
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f35200000000004bd648",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595218,
      "updated": 1777595218
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3efef00000000009a9133",
      "text": "まってこれ誤解を招く字面じゃない？[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777594350,
      "updated": 1777595226
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f35b00000000004bd649",
      "text": "\t対比構造はあるけど「道理を通せば無理を押し込むことになる」の部分だけ切り出して読むとめっちゃ怖い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595226,
      "updated": 1777595265
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f38300000000004bd64a",
      "text": "\t\t[who11.icon]が道理を通すロジックで[who11.icon]の無理を押し込むみたいに見える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595266,
      "updated": 1777595831
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f57f00000000004bd65b",
      "text": "\t\t\tそれは[Summer498.icon]にもロジハラに見える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595775,
      "updated": 1777595787
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f38b00000000004bd64b",
      "text": "\t\tそういう話じゃない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595275,
      "updated": 1777595287
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f39000000000004bd64c",
      "text": "\t[who11.icon]の無理が通れば（公共の）道理が引っ込む（ことわざ）→（逆）（公共の）道理を通せば[who11.icon]の無理が小さくなるように押し込むことになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595280,
      "updated": 1777595895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f43d00000000004bd652",
      "text": "\t\tことわざの方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595452,
      "updated": 1777595458
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f3b000000000004bd64e",
      "text": " \t[} ｵﾗｵﾗｵﾗｵﾗ][********** 無理] /[https://gyazo.com/e0dc75c9592ab7df6c5f5fc56a960c7d]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595311,
      "updated": 1777595465
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f40800000000004bd650",
      "text": "\t\tことわざの逆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595400,
      "updated": 1777595473
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f49b00000000004bd657",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/5e8626c5ce55e1fbe991537c5dc09791][*********** 道理][{ ちゃんとせんか！]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595546,
      "updated": 1777595573
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f49300000000004bd655",
      "text": "\t押し込むという単語を使っている限り字面が悪い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595539,
      "updated": 1777595918
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f60100000000004bd65c",
      "text": "\tちゃんと対等に字面を設定しよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595905,
      "updated": 1777595905
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3f50c00000000004bd659",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777595660,
      "updated": 1777595660
    }
  ]
}